  <div class="news-card-content news-right-box">
    <div itemprop="articleBody">iOS developer Allen Wong has created a third-party app called ‘Remote S for Tesla’ through which users can summon their Tesla cars through their Apple Watches. It also keeps a track of basic information including the car’s charging status, speed and temperature. Notably, Tesla’s &#39;Summon&#39; feature enables the car to unpark itself out of the garage and arrive at the doorstep.</div>
    <div class="news-card-author-time news-card-author-time-in-content">
